description:
This is a 36 minute workout called '30-Minute Yoga For Beginners | Start Yoga Here...' from the channel Yoga With Adriene.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: In this 30-minute session for beginners, we will work with breath and other foundational elements to set you up for a sustainable and beneficial practice you enjoy! Set to a good pace, we will focus on form and function to increase flexibility, build strength, and regulate the nervous system. Repeat this session with consistency and watch your breath and body transform. 

Yoga is for everyone! The hardest part is showing up. 


This class is perfect for all beginners or anyone wanting to move more slowly and mindfully. 


You will move through breath work, poses for the spine, shoulders, and core, as well as standing poses such as warrior two, and more.


Thank you for allowing me to guide you through practice. Let me know how it goes for you in the comment section below!

- - - - - - - - - -
